title: Chong Zheng Tian Ran
description: Chinese name 崇正天然, address 松江区龙马路118弄商业街19号(近地铁9号线松江大学城站). English known as The Authentic Natural. Directions: from Songjiang University Town subway station go down the overpass on the right side, then on the left there is an alley way, go straight you will see Quan Jia supermarket where Commercial Street is.
streetAddress: 19 Commercial Street, 118 Longma Road, Songjiang District
